---
/**
 * @file Hero.astro
 * @description Impacto visual inicial con animaciones de entrada y estética de vanguardia.
 */
---

<div
  class="md:col-span-3 bg-dent-card border border-dent-border rounded-[2.5rem] p-6 sm:p-10 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-end min-h-[450px] md:min-h-[550px] relative overflow-hidden shadow-sm group"
>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] [background-image:linear-gradient(#0ea5e9_1.5px,transparent_1.5px),linear-gradient(90deg,#0ea5e9_1.5px,transparent_1.5px)] [background-size:40px_40px]"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-dent-accent/10 via-transparent to-transparent">
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-80 h-80 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700 hidden lg:block"
  >
    <img
      src="/hero/Corona dental de zirconia y titanio.webp"
      alt="Prótesis de alta precisión"
      class="w-full h-full object-contain animate-float drop-shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(14,165,233,0.3)] group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10">
    <div
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dent-accent/10 border border-dent-accent/20 mb-6 animate-pulse-soft"
    >
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span
          class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-dent-accent opacity-75"
        ></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-dent-accent"></span>
      </span>
      <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-dent-accent"
        >Laboratorio Digital 4.0</span
      >
    </div>

    <h1
      class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-dent-dark leading-[0.85] italic tracking-tighter uppercase"
    >
      Precisión <br />
      <span
        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-dent-accent to-blue-600 animate-gradient"
      >
        Absoluta
      </span>
      <br />
      en cada pieza.
    </h1>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-6 mt-8">
      <p
        class="text-slate-500 max-w-md text-base lg:text-lg font-medium italic leading-tight border-l-2 border-dent-accent/30 pl-4"
      >
        Elevamos el estándar de la prótesis dental mediante flujos <span
          class="text-dent-dark font-bold">CAD/CAM</span
        > y materiales de última generación.
      </p>

      <div
        class="flex gap-8 border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-dent-border pt-6 md:pt-0 md:pl-8"
      >
        <div>
          <span class="block text-2xl font-black text-dent-dark italic">+15k</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-400">Casos Éxito</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block text-2xl font-black text-dent-dark italic">24h</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-400">Logística</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
